image_analysis.description: A photograph showing the interior of a closet. The closet contains a top shelf with a large black bag and several white items in plastic garment bags. Below the shelf is a hanging rod with various items of clothing including dark jackets, a plaid shirt, a black puffer vest, and a white shirt. On the floor of the closet, which has yellow carpeting, there is a woven wicker basket containing dark clothing and several pairs of dark shoes scattered nearby. To the left, a mirrored door reflects the interior. To the right, an open white door with gold-toned hardware (knobs and locks) is visible.
image_analysis.layout: Interior shot of a closet through an open door.

notes: The text 'I\' appears to be a fragment or artifact of the scanning/OCR process. The primary text is the Bates stamp identifier at the bottom right.
